HC3.jpg","release_date":"1991-08-01","vote_average":7.458,"backdrop_path":"/3VTY3ZaP5UDLgfI1z2HJHEgesnA.jpg","original_title":"Barton Fink","original_language":"en"},{"id":307,"adult":false,"title":"Rome, Open City","video":false,"overview":"During the Nazi occupation of 1944 Rome, Resistance leader Giorgio Manfredi is pursued by the Nazis as he seeks refuge and a means of escape.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":1.9657,"vote_count":959,"poster_path":"/ijGV4v8JxgbNzgEhqKdzHdaZn8a.jpg","release_date":"1945-10-08","vote_average":8.019,"backdrop_path":"/cztYhbawTjK9m8lFBd97Yl5Zd8r.jpg","original_title":"Roma città aperta","original_language":"it"},{"id":271312,"adult":false,"title":"Operation Cross Eagles","video":false,"overview":"In Yugoslavia during WWII, a small band of courageous commandoes are sent to kidnap an important German commander in exchange for an American general being held in a German fortress.","genre_ids":[10752],"popularity":0.3227,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/uPonwsdNV1fPrfVLclU5CTl6jaG.jpg","release_date":"1968-01-01","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/oAfNTe4DhEfuu3vIZPZDHrxrXcO.jpg","original_title":"Operation Cross Eagles","original_language":"en"},{"id":238,"adult":false,"title":"The Godfather","video":false,"overview":"Spanning the years 1945 to 1955, a chronicle of the fictional Italian-American Corleone crime family. When organized crime family patriarch, Vito Corleone barely survives an attempt on his life, his youngest son, Michael steps in to take care of the would-be killers, launching a campaign of bloody revenge.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":36.9611,"vote_count":22508,"poster_path":"/3bhkrj58Vtu7enYsRolD1fZdja1.jpg","release_date":"1972-03-14","vote_average":8.687,"backdrop_path":"/tSPT36ZKlP2WVHJLM4cQPLSzv3b.jpg","original_title":"The Godfather","original_language":"en"},{"id":1252826,"adult":false,"title":"Under The Ashes","video":false,"overview":"The Second World War. French authorities ban political parties and unions. In Algeria, the leaders of political and trade union organizations were arrested and interned in \"surveillance\" camps with more than 2,000 French and foreigners: communist activists, trade unionists, brigadists, Spanish republicans and other opponents of the Vichy regime. The Djenien Bourezg camp is one of these camps, located in southern Algeria and is one of the most formidable. An old activist for the Algerian national cause returns to the scene. He blows away the ashes that cover this part of history. And through it, we discover the hard fight of the camp inmates for respect and human dignity, under a fascist command.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":0.1847,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/o5V9eKpGIVqeFAOWjn026geybPb.jpg","release_date":"1990-01-01","vote_average":9,"backdrop_path":"/ovfgbdfl5kro2ES9xqU4PSVbRcA.jpg","original_title":"Sous La Cendre","original_language":"ar"},{"id":1591,"adult":false,"title":"Nowhere in Africa","video":false,"overview":"A Jewish woman named Jettel Redlich flees Nazi Germany with her daughter Regina, to join her husband, Walter, on a farm in Kenya. At first, Jettel refuses to adjust to her new circumstances, bringing with her a set of china dishes and an evening gown. While Regina adapts readily to this new world, forming a strong bond with her father's cook, an African named Owuor.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.7044,"vote_count":178,"poster_path":"/2ED1GaTKhHielGYa1giBsxfoacp.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-11","vote_average":7.07,"backdrop_path":"/7WcWTWOmCNLFnazUmIY64eSvMMz.jpg","original_title":"Nirgendwo in Afrika","original_language":"de"},{"id":1254547,"adult":false,"title":"Strange Tales from a Chinese Studio: Pupil's Language","video":false,"overview":"This film tells the story of scholar Fang Dong who endangers his life because of his greed for beauty, and his kind-hearted Ya who loves Fang Dong deeply and chooses to sacrifice herself in exchange for Fang Dong. The prodigal son Fang Dong embarks on a journey to find his true love, and encounters and rescues an oppressed kind-hearted banshee on the road. With the help of the demon catcher and others, the lovers finally get married, a poignant love story.","genre_ids":[53,10752],"popularity":0.3974,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/l0r4O5B45woX61ci2FJaWEg22W9.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-05","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/6LwSL2kKpIihkulT8iO5KB4TbZ0.jpg","original_title":"聊斋志异之瞳人语","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1654,"adult":false,"title":"The Dirty Dozen","video":false,"overview":"12 American military prisoners in World War II are ordered to infiltrate a well-guarded enemy château and kill the Nazi officers vacationing there. The soldiers, most of whom are facing death sentences for a variety of violent crimes, agree to the mission and the possible commuting of their sentences.","genre_ids":[28,12,10752],"popularity":3.8636,"vote_count":1288,"poster_path":"/tFWWsuhp22zJ6OG6QepJIiPUfeF.jpg","release_date":"1967-06-15","vote_average":7.579,"backdrop_path":"/iXS9Y5oMwbN9wKsVu7mNzsI7QSM.jpg","original_title":"The Dirty Dozen","original_language":"en"},{"id":1715,"adult":false,"title":"The Cider House Rules","video":false,"overview":"Homer is an orphan who was never adopted, becoming the favorite of orphanage director Dr. Larch. Dr. Larch imparts his full medical knowledge on Homer, who becomes a skilled, albeit unlicensed, physician. But Homer yearns for a self-chosen life outside the orphanage. What will Homer learn about life and love in the cider house? What of the destiny that Dr. Larch has planned for him?","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":2.6179,"vote_count":1262,"poster_path":"/qAECAgqjSFRVZzEEGbFAZqZNiDh.jpg","release_date":"1999-12-17","vote_average":7.073,"backdrop_path":"/1bVq5JXx7d4kEx4kctrEzFuiyBo.jpg","original_title":"The Cider House Rules","original_language":"en"},{"id":465502,"adult":false,"title":"Battle of Okinawa in Color","video":false,"overview":"By mid-1945, Hitler is dead and the war has ended in Europe. Halfway around the world, however, the fighting is still going strong on a small island in the Pacific. Okinawa was the site of the last battle of the last great war of the 20th century, with a casualty rate in the tens of thousands. Through it all, military cameramen risked their lives to film the conflict, from brutal land combat to fierce kamikaze attacks at sea. See the footage they captured and experience this intense battle the way the soldiers saw it -- in color.","genre_ids":[99,10752,36],"popularity":0.2948,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/9Heg0z0P6tJ2P3eIuupqGYvZxDF.jpg","release_date":"2017-06-25","vote_average":9,"backdrop_path":"/wDwOGMzUmk6i4EgGJyqfNeaqUxh.jpg","original_title":"Battle of Okinawa in Color","original_language":"en"},{"id":1735,"adult":false,"title":"The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor","video":false,"overview":"Archaeologist Rick O'Connell travels to China, pitting him against an emperor from the 2,000-year-old Han dynasty who's returned from the dead to pursue a quest for world domination. This time, O'Connell enlists the help of his wife and son to quash the so-called 'Dragon Emperor' and his abuse of supernatural power.","genre_ids":[12,28,14],"popularity":6.12,"vote_count":4726,"poster_path":"/A3acM1lX5PNWQa6r5qeMAJOxbnT.jpg","release_date":"2008-07-01","vote_average":5.513,"backdrop_path":"/W034dd7w2malON26KWyZm4y37W.jpg","original_title":"The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor","original_language":"en"},{"id":1771,"adult":false,"title":"Captain America: The First Avenger","video":false,"overview":"During World War II, Steve Rogers is a sickly man from Brooklyn who's transformed into super-soldier Captain America to aid in the war effort. Rogers must stop the Red Skull – Adolf Hitler's ruthless head of weaponry, and the leader of an organization that intends to use a mysterious device of untold powers for world domination.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"popularity":7.3077,"vote_count":22477,"poster_path":"/vSNxAJTlD0r02V9sPYpOjqDZXUK.jpg","release_date":"2011-07-22","vote_average":7.004,"backdrop_path":"/yFuKvT4Vm3sKHdFY4eG6I4ldAnn.jpg","original_title":"Captain America: The First Avenger","original_language":"en"},{"id":1783,"adult":false,"title":"To End All Wars","video":false,"overview":"Based on a real-life story, this drama focuses on a small group of Allied soldiers in Burma who are held captive by the Japanese. Capt. Ernest Gordon, Lt. Jim Reardon and Maj. Ian Campbell are among the military officers kept imprisoned and routinely beaten and deprived of food. While Campbell wants to rebel and attempt an escape, Gordon tries to take a more stoic approach, an attitude that proves to be surprisingly resonant.","genre_ids":[18,10752,28],"popularity":1.3686,"vote_count":177,"poster_path":"/4fXRE02M2EckpGPZNbuZIo05dmL.jpg","release_date":"2001-09-02","vote_average":6.415,"backdrop_path":"/7ew2soLD1RY0PbHwhReqNUv08Wa.jpg","original_title":"To End All Wars","original_language":"en"},{"id":856437,"adult":false,"title":"Farha","video":false,"overview":"Palestine, 1948. After the withdrawal of the British occupiers, tensions rise between Arabs and Jews. Meanwhile, Farha, the smart daughter of the mayor of a small village, unaware of the coming tragedy, dreams of going to study in the big city.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":0.9159,"vote_count":78,"poster_path":"/X4kRsdyP9FgMfKKn9LZiVscZY5.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-14","vote_average":7.167,"backdrop_path":"/fiG2E2FFYtdT8VaL51mHU889yKd.jpg","original_title":"Farha","original_language":"ar"},{"id":2016,"adult":false,"title":"Days of Glory","video":false,"overview":"1943. They have never stepped foot on French soil but because France was at war, Said, Abdelkader, Messaoud and Yassir enlist in the French Army, along with 130,000 other “indigenous” soldiers, to liberate the “fatherland” from the Nazi enemy. Heroes that history has forgotten…","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":1.2185,"vote_count":392,"poster_path":"/d78c7G8wDVGUTWH95tpuEGiK6IZ.